document_data.name: Ooloolar Street
document_data.mainbody: '''Ooloolar Street''' was a street found within [[Tulmon]] along the [[Lake of Steam]] during the mid-to-late 14{{th}} century [[DR]].
document_data.Notable Locations: [[Moonthumb Necessities]], a general goods store that catered to [[adventurer]]s, was located along Ooloolar Street.
